_sText:
This is a new iceworld made from scratch by me. I hope you all enjoy. If anyone wants a private request like this one just ask me! I want to make maps! :P

Features:
-Equal, Fair (symetrical)
-Free weapons with wide variety
-Walk ramps all around the map for NINJAS!

Install:
Extract the map file (fy_iceworld_advanced_gpk.bsp), and the navigation file (many_houses_wcs.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 1.5 Hours

Hope you enjoy!
